{"tid":675331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【錘劫珠寶店】兩匪搶劫海港城珠寶店　破櫥窗奪珠寶手錶後逃去","createTime":"2018-05-23T12:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T16:55:06.000Z","uid":116257,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"733c965e443c77b3a7274fc606dc691e113675aa","tid":675331,"uid":116257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:16:22.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀海港城發生珠寶店劫案，兩名賊人以手錘打破櫥窗，搶走一批珠寶及手錶後逃去。事發晚上7時許，警方接報於尖沙咀海港城內一間珠寶店，有兩名男子打破櫥窗，奪走一批珠寶及手錶後逃去。警方正於現場調查及追查兩匪下落，損失正在點算中。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/191606/錘劫珠寶店-兩匪搶劫海港城珠寶店-破櫥窗奪珠寶手錶後逃去\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F191606%2F%E9%8C%98%E5%8A%AB%E7%8F%A0%E5%AF%B6%E5%BA%97-%E5%85%A9%E5%8C%AA%E6%90%B6%E5%8A%AB%E6%B5%B7%E6%B8%AF%E5%9F%8E%E7%8F%A0%E5%AF%B6%E5%BA%97-%E7%A0%B4%E6%AB%A5%E7%AA%97%E5%A5%AA%E7%8F%A0%E5%AF%B6%E6%89%8B%E9%8C%B6%E5%BE%8C%E9%80%83%E5%8E%BB&d=vpYrFJbs0IQmUCDlfh9O0C7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=399fc370\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/191606/錘劫珠寶店-兩匪搶劫海港城珠寶店-破櫥窗奪珠寶手錶後逃去</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 另一來源： <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180523/bkn-20180523195410340-0523_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180523%2Fbkn-20180523195410340-0523_00822_001.html&d=vpYrFJbs0IQmUCDlfh9O0C7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=ff985a4a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180523/bkn-20180523195410340-0523_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個海港城夜晚人多車又多，可以點走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8529ca15a63c562fefe449207a1e8491433a0133","tid":675331,"uid":116257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:19:37.000Z","msg":"上年9月又係用鎚扑爛櫥窗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170919/mobile/bkn-20170919100938866-0919_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https